stand
Discworld player help
stand

.SH Name
.SI 5
stand - Change your position to standing.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
stand
stand on the floor
stand on <object>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Allows you to change your position.  To stand on the floor, or to stand on
something, or to just stand up if you are sitting.
.EP


.SH Examples
.SI 5
> stand
You stand up.
> stand on the floor
You stand on the floor.
> stand on table
You stand on the table.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
sit, kneel, lie, meditate, crouch
.EP
